11
00:00:48,000 --> 00:00:52,000
Before we start this tutorial, just to make sure everybody is clear.

12
00:00:52,000 --> 00:01:01,000
Offline mode is only to be used for the customers where you do not have a good or stable internet connection.

13
00:01:01,000 --> 00:01:11,000
So if your customer has not good internet connection, then you want to use the offline version only.

14
00:01:11,000 --> 00:01:18,000
So to start off with offline, first up, as you can see on the top right corner is the toggle for online and offline.

15
00:01:18,000 --> 00:01:22,000
So we want to just click on the toggle and you will see this message.

16
00:01:22,000 --> 00:01:25,000
You just want to click yes all the time.

17
00:01:25,000 --> 00:01:27,000
So click yes.

18
00:01:27,000 --> 00:01:31,000
And you can see the first option here is load location.

19
00:01:31,000 --> 00:01:35,000
This is basically to be done online.

20
00:01:35,000 --> 00:01:42,000
So let's say the TSR or the VMI coordinator before going to the customer site.

21
00:01:43,000 --> 00:01:51,000
